@startuml 06_Zoom_Assistant_IA
title Zoom ⑩⑪ — Assistant IA Privacy-First\nPrivacy Gateway · Text-to-SQL · CDM Desk

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceMessageFontSize 11
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9E6
skinparam noteBorderColor #D4A017

actor       "Employé CDM\n(Back Office)" as USER
participant "CDM Desk\n(Next.js)" as FRONT  #EAF3FB
participant "FastAPI\nBackend" as API    #EAF3FB
participant "Privacy Gateway\n(privacy_gateway.py)" as GW #FFD0D0
database    "Mapping\n(PostgreSQL)" as MAP   #FFF9E6
participant "Qwen 2.5 7B ①\n(SQL Generation)" as QWEN1 #F0E8FF
participant "Dremio\n(SQL Engine)" as DREMIO #FFF9E6
participant "Qwen 2.5 7B ②\n(Response Format)" as QWEN2 #F0E8FF

USER  -> FRONT  : "Quelle est la position EUR/MAD ?"
FRONT -> API    : POST /api/ask\n{question: "Position EUR/MAD ?"}

activate API

API   -> GW     : pseudonymize(question)
activate GW
GW    -> MAP    : lookup {EUR/MAD → CCY_ab12}
MAP   --> GW    : mapping {CCY_ab12: "EUR/MAD"}
GW    --> API   : pseudo_question="Position CCY_ab12 ?"\nmapping={CCY_ab12: EUR/MAD}
deactivate GW

note right of GW
  Qwen ① ne voit jamais
  les vraies valeurs CDM
end note

API   -> QWEN1  : generate_sql("Position CCY_ab12 ?")
activate QWEN1
QWEN1 --> API   : SELECT devise, position_mad\nFROM gold.positions_nettes\nWHERE devise = 'CCY_ab12'
deactivate QWEN1

API   -> DREMIO : execute SQL\nWHERE devise = 'CCY_ab12'
activate DREMIO
DREMIO --> API  : [{devise:CCY_ab12, position_mad:490350000}]
deactivate DREMIO

API   -> GW     : deanonymize_data(results, mapping)
activate GW
GW    -> MAP    : reverse lookup {CCY_ab12 → EUR/MAD}
MAP   --> GW    : {EUR/MAD: 490350000}
GW    --> API   : [{devise:EUR/MAD, position_mad:490350000}]
deactivate GW

API   -> QWEN2  : format_response(\n  question="Position EUR/MAD ?",\n  data=[{EUR/MAD: 490350000}]\n)
activate QWEN2
QWEN2 --> API   : "La position nette EUR/MAD est de\n490 350 000 MAD sur 12 deals confirmés."
deactivate QWEN2

API   --> FRONT : {response: "490 350 000 MAD", sql, latency_ms}
deactivate API

FRONT --> USER  : "La position EUR/MAD : 490 350 000 MAD"

note over USER, QWEN2
  Qwen ① : reçoit tokens anonymes → génère SQL
  Qwen ② : reçoit vraies valeurs déjà dépseudonymisées → formate
  Données CDM ne quittent jamais le datacenter
end note

@enduml